1. Requirement
===============
The Service Manager require that OpenNebula is installed and configured.

2. Installation
================
To run the Service Manager, execute:
./INSTALL

3. Configuration
=================
The configuration file is: config.ru

4. Running
===========
To run the Service Manager, execute:
./RUN

the Service Manager is running at: 
[host]:9292

the request interface is at:
[host]:9292/-/

5. Testing
===========
You can test the API with the sandbox at [host]/sandbox

[host] must be replace by your hostname (ex: localhost)

6. Image customization
========================
The image directory is at [Service Manager directory]/images
each immages need to have ruby installed.
